│ the issue is likely introduced by the *first transformation*, or due to incorrect       │
│ analysis information feeding into it.                                                   │
│ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first transformation point* that modifies   │
│ the IR in the pass regardless of whether it's in the                                    │
│ `autofix/build/llvm-build/122558/bin/opt -p loop-vectorize -force-vector-width=2        │
│ -epilogue-vectorization-force-VF=2 -S /tmp/reprod_c7kdfkid.l` module or other modules.  │
